      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "According to the Volusia County Sheriff’s Office, deputies had received a tip from police in Washington that Arthur N. Wilcher of Deltona might be involved in the theft of multiple ",
