      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "From there, deputies conducted surveillance on Wilcher’s home and investigated him for about a month. After gathering enough evidence to move on him, they seized three luxury cars they say were stolen: a 2017 Mercedes-Benz S-Class Coupe, a 2017 ",
