            "style": "",
            "text": " with absolutely awful wheels, and a 2018 Jaguar F-Pace. Wilcher was leaving his house in the BMW when he was arrested.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
