      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Authorities claim the BMW and Mercedes were both stolen in Georgia. As for the Jaguar, it was stolen in Miami Gardens. The National Insurance Crime Bureau was on the scene to conduct its investigation, where they say an agent found all three luxury cars had ",
